column5: Just heard that Jerry Lewis mister comedy has past at 91 yrs.... made a lot of money for MD over the years   RIP Jerry.. MR Clown    My Mistake Fixed it....

My Mistake ... Fixed it  May he rest in peace... And his memory live on...
LOL loonie, since I have MS my focus on the illness may be better? although both suck and the names can run together? He spent a lot of time and effort trying to help regardless.
